## 📁 Project Structure

```
/
├── app/                    # Expo Router pages
│   ├── (auth)/             # Auth-protected routes
│   ├── (tabs)/             # Tab navigation (Inbox, Calendar, Notes, Profile)
│   ├── _layout.tsx         # Root layout (providers, fonts, Supabase)
│   └── index.tsx           # Landing/onboarding
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                 # shadcn/ui-style primitives (Button, Card, Input)
│   ├── features/           # Feature-specific components (CalendarGrid, AIChat)
│   └── shared/             # Shared components (Header, EmptyState, ErrorBoundary)
├── lib/
│   ├── supabase/           # Supabase client, auth, hooks
│   ├── ai/                 # OpenAI wrappers (schedule generator, note parser)
│   ├── design-system.ts    # Design tokens (colors, typography, spacing)
│   └── utils.ts            # Shared utilities
├── types/
│   ├── database.types.ts   # Generated Supabase types
│   └── index.ts            # App-specific types (Schedule, Note, Goal)
├── docs/
│   ├── 01-plan/            # PDCA plans
│   ├── 02-design/          # PDCA designs
│   ├── 03-analysis/        # PDCA gap analyses
│   └── 04-report/          # PDCA completion reports
└── .cursorrules            # This file
```

