## 🎨 Design System

### Colors (Light & Dark Mode)
```typescript
// lib/design-system.ts
export const colors = {
  brand: {
    primary: '#6366F1',    // Indigo-500
    secondary: '#EC4899',  // Pink-500
  },
  text: {
    primary: 'text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100',
    secondary: 'text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400',
    tertiary: 'text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500',
  },
  background: {
    primary: 'bg-white dark:bg-gray-950',
    secondary: 'bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900',
    tertiary: 'bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800',
  },
  border: 'border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800',
}
```

### Typography
- Headings: Inter (English), Pretendard (Korean)
- Body: Same stack
- Code: JetBrains Mono
- Scales: text-xs (12px), text-sm (14px), text-base (16px), text-lg (18px), text-xl (20px), text-2xl (24px)

### Spacing
- Base unit: 4px (Tailwind's 1)
- Consistent: Use space-y-4, gap-6, p-4, etc.
- Screen padding: px-4 (mobile), px-6 (tablet)

### Components
- Primitives from React Native Paper or custom with Tailwind-inspired styling
- Reference: shadcn/ui patterns (Button variants, Card composition, Input states)

