## 🔒 Security & Data

### Environment Variables
```
# Supabase
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxx.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...  # Server-only

# OpenAI
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...              # Server-only

# Stripe
EXPO_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...      # Server-only
```

### Auth Rules
- Supabase RLS enabled on ALL tables
- Row-level policies: users see only their own data
- No direct database access from client; use Supabase client with RLS

### AI Data Handling
- User input sanitized before sending to OpenAI
- AI responses validated with Zod before storage
- No PII sent to AI unless user explicitly consents
- Anonymize data in logs and analytics

